{"tid":1910830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"bn_黑店","createTime":"2020-03-05T02:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T02:53:21.000Z","uid":349236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5ffde90d8e07be19e52ecdadb14f271ed5587eea","tid":1910830,"uid":349236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"呢排好多時大家都會預購<br />\n尤其是口罩<br />\n好希望大家唔好墮入黑店嘅陷阱<br />\n今次為大家介紹呢一間:<br />\n<a href=\"http://Bn_.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FBn_.com.hk&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=8cf932a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Bn_.com.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n佢擁有一條非常不公平條款<br />\n就係如果佢冇貨嘅話呢佢會幫你退錢向佢嗰個購物金到<br />\n俾你下次使用<br />\n但問題係<br />\n如果下次又係冇貨<br />\n又會再推落佢個購物金<br />\n即係一個字<br />\n你係賭一鋪<br />\n賭佢有貨<br />\n咁你就唔使蝕錢啦<br />\n<br />\n已有黑店page:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Bnm%E9%BB%91%E5%BA%97%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-100128361533147/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FBnm%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25BA%2597%25E8%258B%25A6%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-100128361533147%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=b88da116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/Bnm%E9%BB%91%E5%BA%97%E8%8B%A6%E4%B8%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-100128361533147/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家去望望<br />\n尤其是呢牌大家都成日預購貨品<br />\n大家賺嘅都係辛苦錢<br />\n希望呼籲一下親戚朋友唔好再幫襯呢間野"}]}